```

Your folder should look like:
```
first-connect-erp/
├── first_connect_portal.html
└── vercel.json
```

---

## Step 3 — Create a free GitHub account
Go to **github.com** and sign up if you don't have an account

---

## Step 4 — Upload your folder to GitHub
1. Go to **github.com/new** to create a new repository
2. Name it `first-connect-erp`
3. Click **Create repository**
4. Click **uploading an existing file**
5. Drag and drop both files into the upload area
6. Click **Commit changes**

---

## Step 5 — Create a free Vercel account
Go to **vercel.com** and sign up using your GitHub account

---

## Step 6 — Deploy on Vercel
1. On Vercel dashboard click **Add New Project**
2. Find your `first-connect-erp` repository and click **Import**
3. Don't change any settings — just click **Deploy**
4. Wait 30 seconds ⏳

---

## Step 7 — Your ERP is live! 🎉
Vercel will give you a link like:
```
first-connect-erp.vercel.app
